text: Naberezhny () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Khatukayskoye Rural Settlement of Krasnogvardeysky District, Adygea, Russia. The population was 92 as of 2018. There are 3 streets. == Geography == The settlement is located 10 km north-east from Krasnogvardeyskoye, on the left bank of the Kuban River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Krasnogvardeysky District
title: Naberezhny, Republic of Adygea
